| Agent / Workflow | Required MCPs |
|---|---|
| `bug-validator` (Rule 32) | Confluence (Atlassian), Jira (Atlassian), Slack |
| `bulk-bug-validator` (Rule 38) | Confluence (Atlassian), Jira (Atlassian), Slack |
| `hands-off` (Rule 37) | Jira (Atlassian), Confluence (Atlassian), Slack |
